      "body" : "In commit \"test: Call ceildiv helper with integer\" (11d4385819154e637eb34879bf3e4040f85ef194)\r\n\r\nNot directly related to this PR, but it seems like this satoshi_round call does nothing and should be dropped. (I suggested this previously https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22949#discussion_r728064800)",
